    "description": "在本扩展包中，玩家将会体验到以下内容：<br><br><strong>1.七个全新的周边势力</strong><br><i>◇各具特色的武将</i>：三国历史上真实的异族武将将一一登场；<br><i>◇风格迥异的建筑</i>：每个异族据点都有自己独特的建筑样式；<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/18881304647cc0ffebf34b83769accc4.avif?t=1656090806\" width=448 height=226 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/51fd329567a791c5951ad41aec9b238d.avif?t=1656090806\" width=450 height=226 /></span><br><br><i>◇全新的兵种</i>：大牂、烧当、高阙、盛乐、平刚骑兵，南野步兵，对马武士<br><i>◇全新的战场</i>：四张具有浓郁异族风情的野战战；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/0a662848c7a6d2b89cadc9b4fd412518.avif?t=1656090806\" width=800 height=574 /></span><br><br><i>◇全新的玩法</i>：可在外交中与异族亲善，也可在谋略中请求异族部队攻伐其他敌对势力。<br><i>◇边疆的侵扰</i>：如果处理不好和异族势力的关系，他们会持续侵扰与其相邻的边关城市，极大的影响城市发展，甚至将城市夷为平地……<br><i>◇永不消亡</i>：异族势力城市无法占领，其势力只会短暂屈从，之后又会卷土重来（不可灭亡）；<br><br><strong>2.十二个山寨匪患</strong><br><i>◇历史武将</i>： 山寨中除了拥有一般的NPC武将外，还会根据史实，出现一些历史武将；<br><i>◇历史武将可招募</i>：战斗胜利，山寨中的历史武将有几率会投奔；<br><i>◇不同风格的山寨类型</i>：西北、中原、南中山寨，还有江边的水寨；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/b617771fe847d7d37a94c9f2a9ee6f37.avif?t=1656090806\" width=442 height=224 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/bbed71c4b1d14e541dbbade10d5b8e33.avif?t=1656090806\" width=448 height=228 /></span><br><br><i>◇全新的战场</i>：五张不同地域的匪患战场<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/1b8b46591839f91e4fe2f28b932644bf.avif?t=1656090806\" width=800 height=574 /></span><br><br><i>◇骚扰城市</i>：匪患会对其相邻的城市附加一个debuff效果，会降低城市钱粮收益，此外匪患也有一定几率攻击城市，若守备不力，城市会被攻陷；<br><i>◇永不消亡</i>：匪患山寨无法占领，将其攻陷后呈“废弃”状态，之后随时间推移，有一定几率重新出现；<br><br><strong>3.四大神兽副本</strong><br><i>◇野外副本</i>：在大地图上引入全新的野外副本系统，玩家可以自由出征讨伐；<br><i>◇天之四灵</i>：中国远古四大神兽青龙、白虎、朱雀、玄武将以副本BOSS的形式出现在游戏中；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/f29c3ab887aba409d4b7f99fedc27ff0.avif?t=1656090806\" width=204 height=188 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/1a71c665b3baacf6f5c06a0036b9f1f4.avif?t=1656090806\" width=202 height=174 /></span><br><br><i>◇全新的战场</i>：四张契合神兽特性的副本战场；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/290eb412b0122f5a15a0f04b02a23596.avif?t=1656090806\" width=800 height=574 /></span><br><br><i>◇独特的技能</i>：每个神兽都有自己独特而强大的技能；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/08928ab2c60e6f4e2690287af8e2cfc0.poster.avif?t=1656090806\" width=720 height=1080 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/08928ab2c60e6f4e2690287af8e2cfc0.webm?t=1656090806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/08928ab2c60e6f4e2690287af8e2cfc0.mp4?t=1656090806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/ae88eee20e213919b84b599373df35d8.poster.avif?t=1656090806\" width=720 height=1080 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520720/extras/ae88eee20e213919b84b599373df35d8